graph TB
    subgraph Platform ["IW AI Core Platform"]
        DB[(PostgreSQL\nState & History)]
        Daemon[Orchestration\nDaemon]
        Dashboard[Web Dashboard]
        CLI[iw CLI]
    end

    subgraph Projects ["Registered Projects"]
        P1[Project A]
        P2[Project B]
        P3[Project C]
    end

    subgraph Agents ["AI Agents"]
        A1[Claude Code]
        A2[OpenCode]
    end

    Human([Engineering\nTeam]) -->|designs & approves| Dashboard
    Dashboard <-->|reads & controls| DB
    Daemon <-->|polls & updates| DB
    Daemon -->|launches agents in| Projects
    A1 & A2 -->|iw step-start\niw step-done| CLI
    CLI -->|writes state| DB
    Daemon -->|merges to main| Projects

    style Platform fill:#F1F5F9,stroke:#3B82F6,stroke-width:2px
    style Projects fill:#D1FAE5,stroke:#10B981,stroke-width:2px
    style Agents fill:#DBEAFE,stroke:#3B82F6,stroke-width:2px
